    <updated>2018-05-15T09:37:12.042Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="标题"><a href="#标题" class="headerlink" title="标题"></a>标题</h1><hr><figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="section"># 一级标题</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="section">## 二级标题</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="section"># *号与下划线的效果是一样的</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="emphasis">***</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="emphasis">*斜体*</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="emphasis">_斜体_</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="strong">**粗体**</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="strong">__粗体__</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="strong">***斜粗体**</span>*</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="strong">___斜粗体__</span>_</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h1 id="无序列表"><a href="#无序列表" class="headerlink" title="无序列表"></a>无序列表</h1><hr><figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="bullet">* </span>星号表示无序列表</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="bullet">+ </span>加号也能实现无序列表</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="bullet">- </span>减号也能实现无序列表</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h1 id="有序列表"><a href="#有序列表" class="headerlink" title="有序列表"></a>有序列表</h1><hr><figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="bullet">1. </span>数字实现有序列表</span><br><span class="line"><span class="bullet">2. </span>数字实现有序列表</span><br><span class="line"><span class="bullet">3. </span>数字实现有序列表</span><br><span class="line"><span class="bullet">-  </span>接下来用减号就能实现有序了</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h1 id="转义"><a href="#转义" class="headerlink" title="转义"></a>转义</h1><hr><figure class="highlight lsl"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="number">1</span>\. <span class="number">1</span>后面的点为了避免转成有序列表，在.前面加上反斜杠就行</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h1 id="分割线"><a href="#分割线" class="headerlink" title="分割线"></a>分割线</h1><hr><figure class="highlight asciidoc"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="bullet">* </span>三个减号能实现分割线的效果</span><br><span class="line"><span class="bullet">* </span>三个<span class="strong">*号也能实现分割线的效果</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h1 id="区域引用"><a href="#区域引用" class="headerlink" title="区域引用"></a>区域引用</h1><hr><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="meta">&gt;</span><span class="bash"> 区块引用用一个小于号就行了</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">&gt;</span><span class="bash"> 同时还可以使用嵌套引用，用两个小于号，比如说：</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">&gt;</span><span class="bash">&gt; 用了两个小于号就能看到嵌套的效果，同理如果还有在加的话就用三个小于号</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h1 id="代码区块"><a href="#代码区块" class="headerlink" title="代码区块"></a>代码区块</h1><hr><figure class="highlight livescript"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">实现代码区块有两种方式：</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="number">1</span><span class="string">\.</span> 加入四个空格</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">比如说加了四个空格后的效果  </span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="number">2</span><span class="string">\.</span> 加一个制表符</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">加一个制表符后的效果</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h1 id="链接"><a href="#链接" class="headerlink" title="链接"></a>链接</h1><hr><figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">链接用markdown写的格式有几种，但是其写法掌握其中一种就行， 其格式如下：</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="code">`[linkText](link)`</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">例如：</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">[<span class="string">百度</span>](<span class="link">http://www.baidu.com</span>)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h1 id="图片"><a href="#图片" class="headerlink" title="图片"></a>图片</h1><hr><figure class="highlight livecodeserver"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">用markdown完成图片的展示格式如下：</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">* 一个惊叹号 `!`</span><br><span class="line">* 接着一个方括号，里面放上图片的替代文字</span><br><span class="line">* 接着一个普通括号，里面放上图片的网址，最后还可以用引号包住并加上 选择性的 <span class="string">'title'</span> 文字。</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">比如：</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">![Alt <span class="keyword">text</span>](/path/<span class="built_in">to</span>/img.jpg)</span><br><span class="line">![Alt <span class="keyword">text</span>](/path/<span class="built_in">to</span>/img.jpg <span class="string">"Optional title"</span>)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h1 id="markdown-下面这些符号是需要转义的"><a href="#markdown-下面这些符号是需要转义的" class="headerlink" title="markdown 下面这些符号是需要转义的"></a>markdown 下面这些符号是需要转义的</h1><hr><figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">\   反斜线</span><br><span class="line">`   反引号</span><br><span class="line"><span class="bullet">*   </span>星号</span><br><span class="line">_   底线</span><br><span class="line">&#123;&#125;  花括号</span><br><span class="line">[]  方括号</span><br><span class="line">()  括弧</span><br><span class="line"><span class="section">#   井字号</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="bullet">+   </span>加号</span><br><span class="line"><span class="bullet">-   </span>减号</span><br><span class="line">.   英文句点</span><br><span class="line">!   惊叹号</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h1 id="总结"><a href="#总结" class="headerlink" title="总结"></a>总结</h1><p>网络上markdown的文章都是长篇大论的， 看得实在太累，所以我抽了点时间，总结了平时写markdown用得比较多的一些标签的用法</p>]]></content>
    
